                "NextAnswerId": 1,
                "QuestionText_Unsafe": "Imagine you find yourself in the following situation.<br /><br />\n\nAs part of a group project, your team is required to submit a 200-word essay.\nYour teammate, Brandon, is responsible for writing this essay. He sent you his\ndraft, but also admitted that he used an LLM to generate it. He tried assuring\nyou that the LLM he used is a new one, designed to have a very human-like\nwriting style. <br /><br />\n\nHowever, this puts your group at risk. Your professor has expressed concerns\nabout students using LLMs to complete assignments. You don't want to make your\nprofessor suspicious and you are worried that Brandon's essay could be\nidentified as AI-generated, which would negatively affect the entire group.\n<br /><br />\n\n<strong>Your task</strong> is to edit Brandon's essay so that it reads\nconvincingly as human-written and is unlikely to be identified as LLM-generated.\n<br /><br />\n\nTo get a better sense of the writing style of this LLM, you first generate three\nsample essays using it. They are shown below.<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_1_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_1_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>Scientists have identified 91 volcanoes that  buried deep beneath the Antarctic Ice Sheet (these were known before), dramatically reshaping our understanding of the frozen continent\u2019s geology. The discoveries, made using ice-penetrating radar and satellite data, shows a big volcanic province stretching across West Antarctica and they have peaks ranging from 100 meters to nearly 4,000 meters in height. </p>\n           <p>Researchers say the hidden chain rivals some of the world\u2019s most active volcanic regions in scale, though it remains unclear how many of the volcanoes are dormant or potentially active and most are actually concealed beneath, up to, two kilometers of ice making direct observation impossible without advanced imaging technology.</p>\n           <p>These findings bring to our attention some important questions about the stability of the Antarctic Ice Sheet and worryingly scientists warn that geothermal heat from volcanic activity could increase melting from below, potentially influencing global sea level rise.  The discovery also offers new insight into Antarctica\u2019s tectonic history, however experts are stating however that more research is required to determine whether any of the volcanoes pose an immediate threat.</p>\n           <p>Taking this all together means that the region may be more geologically dynamic than previously believed and therefore researchers plan further surveys to map the area in greater detail whilst they also plan to assess how subglacial volcanic systems interact with the ice above.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_2_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_2_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>On Tuesday company officials confirmed a significant leadership shake up at Uber Technologies following the release of an internal investigation into workplace misconduct and compliance failures. The initial probe was launched after a series of employee complaints and regulatory inquiries uncovered lapses in oversight, inconsistent enforcement of company policies and failures in reporting procedures.</p>\n           <p>Three senior executives, including the head of regional operations, have stepped down and two others have been placed on administrative leave pending further review. An interim compliance chief has been appointed to strengthen accountability measures.</p>\n           <p>Chief Executive Dara Khosrowshahi stated the findings were \u201cdeeply concerning\u201d and pledged to implement sweeping reforms, adding that Uber are \"committed to rebuilding trust with our employees, drivers, riders, and regulators.\"</p>\n           <p>As a result of the report there has been renewed scrutiny from transportation regulators in many major cities, where Uber's operating licenses are subject to periodic review. Industry analysts say the shake-up could temporarily disrupt operations but may ultimately position the company for more stable growth if reforms are effectively implemented.</p>\n           <p>Uber shares have closed down three percent since the announcement .</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_3_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_3_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t__PRIME_3_PARAGRAPHS_HTML__\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\n<br />\nWith these samples in mind, you now turn to <strong>Brandon's essay</strong>:\n<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">Brandon's essay</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__STIMULUS_TOPIC__</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n           <p>Barbara Bush, the former first lady of the United States and matriarch of one of the country\u2019s most prominent political families, has died at the age of 92. A family member has confirmed that Barbara passed away piecefully at her home in Houston, surrounded by loved ones.</p>\n           <p>Barbara was the wife of the 41st president, George H.W. and served as the first lady from 1989 to 1993.  Barbara was known for her trademark white hair, sharp wit and outspoken advocacy for literacy. She founded the Barbara Bush Foundation for Family Litercay in 1989, helping raise millions of dollars to promote programs nationwide.</p>\n           <p>She was born in New York City in 1925 by the name Barbara Pierce, she married  in 1945 and raised six children, including former President George W. Bush and former Florida Governor Jeb Bush. She was widely regarded as a reassuring presence within the Bush family and a genuine voice in American politics.</p>\n           <p>Tributes poured in praising her dedication to public service, family and country. Funeral arrangements are expected to be announced in the coming days. She will be remembered for her resilience and quiet dignity throughout her life.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n",
                "QuestionJS": false
            }
        },
